reviewText:
Only one dvd Freakdorm 3 plays on my dvd player the other one Measure up is a much, much better "movie"
ha, ha, but only plays on my computer, lame. I won't buy anymore adult titles from Amazon.com
both are bootlegged dvds, oh well. I am keeping them, but won't order off Amazon.com for
adult products. Measure Up is a good flick, Freadorm 3 is just okay, I'd say don't
waste your cash on these, not up to par.
